OL,3,CFamily informed of 'crime' involving
OL,4,Cchurchyard grave
OL,6,FPolice are investigating reports of an
OL,7,Fundisclosed "crime" at a graveyard in
OL,8,Fa South Yorkshire village.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to the church
OL,11,Fyard connected to All Saints Church,
OL,12,FLaughton-en-le-Morthen, near Rotherham
OL,13,Fon Sunday 1 February.
OL,15,FSouth Yorkshire Police said
OL,16,Fallegations had been made "relating to
OL,17,Fone grave within the church yard".
OL,19,FThe force did not provide further
OL,20,Fdetails of the alleged offence.
