OL,3,CFamily informed of 'crime' involving
OL,4,Cchurchyard grave
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "The next-of-kin
OL,7,Fof the deceased has been informed, and
OL,8,Fthey are being supported by specially-
OL,9,Ftrained family liaison officers.
OL,11,F"The church yard is currently closed
OL,12,Fto members of the public but will be
OL,13,Freopened once we have completed our
OL,14,Finitial enquiries.
OL,16,F"We understand this may be distressing
OL,17,Ffor those whose loved ones are buried
OL,18,Fin the church yard so would like to
OL,19,Foffer reassurance that we currently
OL,20,Fbelieve this was a targeted incident
OL,21,Fand there is no threat to other graves.
